a gas station for the first time.

22:49.405 --> 22:51.240
- Yes. - OK.

22:51.265 --> 22:54.350
It's quite simple.
So don't worry.

22:55.440 --> 22:57.995
- Do you want to come and see here?
- Yes.

22:59.929 --> 23:04.348
This cash register.
This is a barcode reader.

23:04.607 --> 23:08.425
You read the barcode and press
this button and this button.

23:08.547 --> 23:12.789
And those who buy gasoline must come in.
Because the pumps are old, not automatic.

23:14.506 --> 23:16.375
I'm also going to buy a pack of cigarettes.

23:16.619 --> 23:18.111
OK.

23:19.178 --> 23:21.554
Identity verification is
accurate because 12 at a time.

23:21.578 --> 23:24.258
... I was in trouble for selling
a cigarette to someone old.

23:24.552 --> 23:27.404
- Did you sell a cigarette
to a 12 year old boy? - Yes.

23:27.658 --> 23:31.283
Yes, but he had breasts.
So I am confused.

23:34.140 --> 23:36.506
Do you want to spend what you bought?

23:38.285 --> 23:40.540
- Of course. - Okay.

23:41.911 --> 23:44.099
Ask if he has a credit or debit card.

23:44.124 --> 23:46.201
Is that a credit or debit card?

23:46.237 --> 23:48.056
- ATM card. - OK.

23:48.967 --> 23:51.967
It keeps 9.75.

23:59.416 --> 24:02.455
You see, it's that simple.
Bravo.

24:02.502 --> 24:04.182
- Yes. - Okay.

24:04.207 --> 24:08.111
I'll get you a key and let
the rest of the shop go.

24:08.147 --> 24:09.935
- OK. - OK.

24:14.949 --> 24:16.491
Nice man.

24:16.608 --> 24:19.073
For someone who works at the gas station.

24:19.626 --> 24:22.860
Are you gonna stay here all night?

24:23.047 --> 24:25.016
No, I'm going.

24:25.117 --> 24:27.891
I wanted to make sure
everything was okay.

24:28.437 --> 24:30.218
Everything is alright.

24:31.147 --> 24:33.230
Then I'll call
you and check you.

24:33.255 --> 24:34.450
OK.

24:36.348 --> 24:38.005
And don't be too drunk.

24:38.322 --> 24:39.830
You have to pick me up at six.

24:39.859 --> 24:42.293
When was I so drunk?

24:48.472 --> 24:54.183
Translation: aytug2001

25:25.530 --> 25:26.995
Fuck!

25:51.887 --> 25:53.903
We only have five channels.

25:54.572 --> 25:57.843
No problem.
I won't be watching that much TV.

25:58.139 --> 26:03.993
Now it is, but you will be begging
to find a fictional series at 3am.

26:04.375 --> 26:06.094
Believe me.

26:06.353 --> 26:09.603
Okay.  Here are the keys to the store.

26:09.628 --> 26:12.947
This opens the round front
door, okay?

26:12.972 --> 26:16.791
So when you leave the market,
use it to lock the door.

26:16.904 --> 26:20.805
This weak one opens the
back door and the sink door.

26:20.830 --> 26:23.634
I always keep that door closed.

26:25.014 --> 26:26.544
What's that for?

26:27.366 --> 26:29.073
What do you think it's for?

26:29.650 --> 26:31.314
The sink outside?

26:32.864 --> 26:34.563
You learn fast.

26:35.920 --> 26:38.325
Well, I think this is enough.

26:39.554 --> 26:41.940
I think you are ready for your first night.

26:42.882 --> 26:46.499
It will be a stagnant night.
It is always on Monday.

26:53.889 --> 26:57.797
If you have a problem,
give me a call, okay?

26:58.182 --> 27:00.920
Edited everything later
in the evening...

27:00.944 --> 27:03.683
... wants me to
check that it's okay.

27:03.737 --> 27:06.565
- OK.
- Any other issues before you go?

27:09.413 --> 27:11.975
Has this place ever been robbed?

27:14.254 --> 27:17.295
Thing...

27:20.771 --> 27:22.873
Only by me.

27:23.580 --> 27:25.869
You can eat and drink anything you want.

27:25.963 --> 27:30.055
Just keep your hands
away from these babies.

27:30.103 --> 27:32.368
- I don't want to, thank you.
- OK.

27:32.513 --> 27:35.708
Ed doesn't know,
just throw the trash in the back.

27:38.421 --> 27:40.749
And if you smoke, smoke outside.

27:41.146 --> 27:42.389
OK.

27:44.638 --> 27:46.177
I think that's it.

27:46.648 --> 27:48.483
Goodbye, Mary.

27:48.617 --> 27:50.061
I will see.

27:53.502 --> 27:55.404
I hate the rain.

28:46.656 --> 28:48.023
Disgusting.

29:23.363 --> 29:25.051
The brain is ready.

29:26.757 --> 29:29.006
- The patient is also ready.
- Beautiful.

32:26.593 --> 32:27.921
Hi?

33:27.339 --> 33:29.041
Deer gas station. I am Mary.

33:29.066 --> 33:30.690
How long are you open until the evening?

33:31.035 --> 33:33.698
- We are open 24 hours.
- Thank you.

33:47.817 --> 33:51.027
- Deer gas station. I am Mary.
- How long are you open until the evening?

33:52.439 --> 33:54.282
Didn't you just call?

34:19.786 --> 34:21.811
Deer gas station.  I am Mary.

34:22.070 --> 34:23.844
How long are you open until the evening?

34:24.168 --> 34:26.849
Call...
You like to watch people die.

34:55.525 --> 34:57.932
Hi, I am Debbie.
Thanks for calling.

34:57.957 --> 35:00.237
Hi Deb. Only me.

35:00.782 --> 35:04.340
Can you call me on the number I have left?
I need to talk to you.

36:16.914 --> 36:18.531
Behave yourself.

36:34.072 --> 36:35.642
Damn.

36:54.132 --> 36:55.292
Hi.

36:55.360 --> 36:56.868
- Hi. - Ed here?

36:57.291 --> 36:59.075
No, it won't be until tomorrow.

37:01.787 --> 37:04.006
I'll fill it. Diesel.

37:05.761 --> 37:08.026
Pump number two?

37:08.342 --> 37:10.037
Yes Madam.

37:11.121 --> 37:12.738
OK.

37:49.761 --> 37:51.737
A bad night to be out.

37:51.897 --> 37:54.194
Let me say that a lot.

37:54.881 --> 37:56.936
I've never seen you here.

37:57.086 --> 37:59.360
This is my first night.

38:00.782 --> 38:02.274
Did you like it?

38:02.553 --> 38:04.350
Yes sure.

38:04.516 --> 38:07.086
So why is this here?
Are you a student or something?

38:07.208 --> 38:08.411
No.

38:10.948 --> 38:13.776
It was time to hire
a beautiful person.

38:15.311 --> 38:18.693
Why a beautiful
woman like you...

38:19.778 --> 38:21.520
... works in such a mess?

38:22.217 --> 38:23.600
I needed work.

38:24.257 --> 38:26.405
Have your boyfriend look at you.

38:26.654 --> 38:28.346
I do not have a boyfriend.

38:31.990 --> 38:34.091
How comes?

38:34.187 --> 38:38.503
Because I tried to kill him.
Got 159.75, please.

38:43.579 --> 38:46.564
Damn.
I think I'm falling in love.

38:47.709 --> 38:50.647
- Is it a debit or credit card?
- Credit.

38:53.774 --> 38:57.008
When you're tired of not
having a man with you

38:57.901 --> 39:00.143
... I don't sleep for 24 hours.

39:01.329 --> 39:04.851
Thanks, but I'm not going
out with anyone for now.

39:09.268 --> 39:11.471
Shame about those machines.

39:28.491 --> 39:29.855
Damn!

39:34.078 --> 39:36.555
You forgot your credit card!

40:08.522 --> 40:11.095
Oh my God!

40:13.187 --> 40:16.832
- What are you doing here?
- I called you, but you didn't hear.

40:16.952 --> 40:18.268
Yes, I have not heard.

40:18.293 --> 40:21.679
- What are you doing outside?
Someone forgot his credit card.

40:22.415 --> 40:24.462
- Damn.
- God, your lip is bleeding.

40:24.487 --> 40:27.434
Yeah what happened, you hit my face.
Sorry.

40:27.725 --> 40:30.100
- Let's go inside. - Yes.

40:34.012 --> 40:36.473
He had a solid right hook.

40:36.766 --> 40:39.977
Sorry,
I thought you were someone else.

40:40.002 --> 40:42.219
I wouldn't want to be that person.

40:42.443 --> 40:43.662
Yes.

40:44.240 --> 40:45.670
You wouldn't want to.

40:47.586 --> 40:49.547
Are you hurt?

40:49.810 --> 40:51.309
No problem.

40:51.785 --> 40:53.176
Sorry.

40:56.298 --> 40:59.283
So what are you doing here?

40:59.602 --> 41:02.727
Ed asked me to come and see you.

41:05.426 --> 41:06.869
How are you?

41:06.894 --> 41:10.923
I had one customer.

41:13.294 --> 41:14.321
Do you know him?

41:14.346 --> 41:17.836
- A big, tall, bald man driving a truck
- Yes, he is.

41:17.907 --> 41:20.741
Yes, he left it here on purpose.

41:20.999 --> 41:22.999
Why would he do such a thing?

41:23.140 --> 41:28.077
Because Ed slept with this
girl until he hit him.

41:29.978 --> 41:32.908
How can someone sleep with him?

41:33.971 --> 41:35.838
He gave him money.

41:37.088 --> 41:39.510
Disgusting.

41:39.793 --> 41:41.878
They did it in that chair.

41:50.151 --> 41:52.143
How is everything going?

41:56.425 --> 41:57.909
I am fine.

41:58.672 --> 42:00.742
Ed told me he went to jail.

42:02.161 --> 42:03.770
Turn right.

42:03.879 --> 42:06.559
That's why he asked
you to look at me.

42:06.999 --> 42:08.734
To make sure I don't
steal anything.

42:08.759 --> 42:11.780
No, he just wondered
if everything is okay.

42:12.626 --> 42:13.728
Eee?

42:14.337 --> 42:16.892
Looking from here looks good.

42:23.746 --> 42:26.011
Can I ask you a question?

42:28.485 --> 42:29.782
Of course.

42:30.516 --> 42:33.914
Why did you burn your friend?

42:42.633 --> 42:44.821
I think the news spread immediately.

42:51.686 --> 42:53.616
You really want to know?

42:54.546 --> 42:56.468
Do you want to talk?

42:59.541 --> 43:01.401
Not really.

43:02.291 --> 43:03.971
Good.

43:07.911 --> 43:09.958
My boyfriend...

43:11.959 --> 43:14.256
... James Lincoln Fields idi.

43:15.863 --> 43:17.426
Did you fall in the rain?

43:19.608 --> 43:20.788
Yes.

43:21.424 --> 43:24.416
- He killed 30 women. - 35.

43:28.087 --> 43:30.829
So you are also the "audience".

43:31.574 --> 43:32.863
Yes.

43:34.370 --> 43:36.089
The press told me that.

43:38.416 --> 43:41.001
Watched all those
girls get killed?

43:43.052 --> 43:44.700
Not all.

43:45.787 --> 43:47.802
How did he feel?

43:53.273 --> 43:55.281
Like I want to die.

44:00.229 --> 44:02.658
I still want to die every day.

44:03.191 --> 44:05.792
- You don't have to talk about it.
- No problem.

44:09.199 --> 44:11.347
How did you learn?

44:12.675 --> 44:15.234
- Did you...
- Did you kill someone?

44:20.371 --> 44:22.254
Can I take a sip of that?

44:23.785 --> 44:25.074
Thank you.

44:38.129 --> 44:40.575
One night I came home from work.

44:41.274 --> 44:42.766
And...

44:44.374 --> 44:45.945
The house smelled.

44:46.904 --> 44:48.326
So bad.

44:51.689 --> 44:54.650
An animal or a
blocked sewer pipe...

44:55.406 --> 44:58.149
I thought...

45:00.185 --> 45:03.859
I went to the basement and...

45:07.225 --> 45:08.975
... flooded everywhere.

45:14.136 --> 45:16.003
Koku...

45:17.435 --> 45:19.739
... seemed unbearable, so...

45:21.110 --> 45:24.079
... I was about to go
upstairs to call James.

45:25.292 --> 45:26.768
Later...

45:29.301 --> 45:31.219
I saw corpses.

45:34.931 --> 45:36.564
Then I got it.

45:37.156 --> 45:41.750
He buried bodies under our house.

45:43.222 --> 45:45.886
I turned my back to call James.

45:48.702 --> 45:50.702
He was waiting for me.

45:53.502 --> 45:55.584
Have you understood the situation?

46:00.458 --> 46:04.559
I always knew something was going
on, but...

46:07.547 --> 46:09.945
I guess I didn't want to believe it.

46:23.094 --> 46:24.547
What did you do after that?

46:28.789 --> 46:29.907
Nothing.

46:32.367 --> 46:34.758
I remained an audience for what happened.

46:35.992 --> 46:39.696
Why didn't you run away
or go to the police?

46:42.415 --> 46:44.188
He said he would kill me.

46:45.075 --> 46:47.067
And my whole family.

46:49.575 --> 46:52.622
I'm not making excuses for what I
did, but...

46:54.951 --> 46:56.660
I was young.

46:57.419 --> 46:59.299
And I was scared.

47:01.051 --> 47:03.410
I didn't know what else I could do.

47:10.789 --> 47:12.851
Then he showed me.

47:16.214 --> 47:18.230
What happened when you stopped watching?

47:20.057 --> 47:23.393
His name was Christine Rogers.

47:26.472 --> 47:28.269
He was very young.

47:28.871 --> 47:32.355
After that I didn't
want to live anymore.

47:34.132 --> 47:35.608
So...

47:37.285 --> 47:39.068
While he slept...

47:40.882 --> 47:42.865
I set the house on fire.

47:45.726 --> 47:47.452
If you are in it?

47:54.583 --> 47:56.551
Still alive, right?

48:00.179 --> 48:01.921
Why rain?

48:02.913 --> 48:05.662
So that their spirits can be cleaned.

48:15.757 --> 48:17.671
I was very sick.

48:20.530 --> 48:22.936
What's not real...

48:24.184 --> 48:26.064
... I couldn't distinguish.

48:29.072 --> 48:32.791
I saw victims everywhere.

48:35.298 --> 48:37.188
How are you now?

48:41.195 --> 48:43.125
Good day or bad.

48:45.243 --> 48:47.024
But I'm getting better.

48:48.050 --> 48:49.753
It's good to hear that.

48:59.210 --> 49:00.827
This one...

49:01.630 --> 49:04.904
... if you don't tell anyone?

49:05.525 --> 49:08.681
